high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall, then left into the small bathroom.
Remove the knife from the cabinet on the wall.
Turn around and exit the room, then right to go to the wall, then right to exit the bedroom, then right again to the small room with the table in the corner.
Slice the lemon on the table.
Exit this room the way you came in and go to the sink straight ahead and to the right.
Place the knife in the sink.
Go back to the sliced lemon.
Pick up one slice of the lemon.
Go back to the sink you put the knife in.
Wash the lemon slice in the sink with water and pick it back up.
Return to the bedroom you began in.
Place the lemon slice on the small circular table next to the bed.
